description:
Duff Till Dawn - Season 1, Episode 3




Castle Clash!

Who will win this game of cake as Duff Goldman pits two teams of bakers to joust for the golden whisk? Whose castle will withstand the siege of flavor: Jackie McGrath's medieval manor or the whimsy of Reva Alexander-Hawk's sugary stronghold? Duff along with guest judges Sherry Yard and Alysia Reiner will answer all of these questions and crown one team victorious.




Original Air Date: 12-Feb-2015
